{"tid":1865828,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《一公升的眼淚》重溫澤尻戲劇般的成長","createTime":"2020-02-06T11:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T13:06:30.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0dc4866319a304af30d0ba6d91a369617d47f20","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/feat1_16070369075c0f9106c94d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Ffeat1_16070369075c0f9106c94d0.png&h=46080cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n33歲的她於2019年11月16日因涉毒被捕，上月31日在東京地方法院首度開庭審訊，庭上她承認藏毒及吸毒罪，更表示不計劃重返演藝圈，等於發表引退宣言。最終澤尻被判監禁1年半，獲緩刑3年，不用入獄。"},{"pid":"599edf2c398591e7482854eaf0341e30457ab992","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"2005播出的日劇《一公升的眼淚》這個名字。當時扮演池內亞也的澤尻繪里香有著一副清純精緻的外貌，對抗病魔時真摯的演技和眼淚，深深打動觀眾，她的人氣也迎來大爆發。"},{"pid":"33bef2a54c2a2e4c6c6316902b210d629577820f","tid":1865828,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f06b9f3679678b05f4d9dd495bc2fd5b1a6f82a","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-10-6.04.50_15073656815c0e38a7e5f66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-10-6.04.50_15073656815c0e38a7e5f66.jpg&h=84c7159f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TZTu2ek16d4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTZTu2ek16d4&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsndC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=2953070f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TZTu2ek16d4</a><br />\n<br />\n隨著人氣的急升，她陸陸續續接了很多部作品，而在飾演日劇《太陽之歌》的雨音薰時，澤尻繪里香以角色歌手的身份出了一張單曲，更成為年度女藝人單曲售賣排行冠軍，歌演兩棲成績驚人。"},{"pid":"2faeabc512c69d45db5ad06440fb184184af280b","tid":1865828,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"下海?"},{"pid":"af1e5b4b0a6f3631ff626d67c253b80c6ed86244","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/95VEtDzPsdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F95VEtDzPsdE&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsndC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=4b21272c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/95VEtDzPsdE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZA2WrFURqfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZA2WrFURqfI&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsndC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=7f0c29e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZA2WrFURqfI</a><br />\n<br />\n澤尻繪里香自此成為八卦雜誌的話題，到處都是她在夜店爛醉等醜聞，由於處事態度，她成為大家心中的「惡女」。2009年，澤尻英龍華與大22歲的高城剛閃電結婚，並且創立工作室，但經營不善，關係破裂，於1年又3個月後決定離婚，經歷兩年的離婚官司，終於簽字畫上句號。"},{"pid":"d2ffe5d57bffe78e7e1841291c566e0c9c83d30b","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"清純的形象深入民心，然而溫柔可愛的她在2007年就好像進入反叛期一般，在《塵封筆記本》的宣傳會上，她一上台就保持一個冷漠的態度，20分鐘的宣傳只是短短三句話，讓場面一度尷尬。之後在電視直播的節目上，面對大牌主持人中山秀征時，經常冷笑看指甲，不耐煩的心情在表露無遺。"},{"pid":"bb933cc7d71477aa1ffb70b4c86ef98baa21e734","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-10-6.12.28_12748044375c0e3a708ff2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-10-6.12.28_12748044375c0e3a708ff2c.jpg&h=74b10734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有「惡女」形象的她自2007開始，多次成為《文春》評選最討厭的女星裏面的第一位，雖然她屢獲差評，但是在最想要的女星長相排名中，她同樣是前幾名，被人們所嚮往著。"},{"pid":"ad11e0f0946cf402485bb06ccac8053e15b015cf","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-10-6.08.54_15608755115c0e399dc3f35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-10-6.08.54_15608755115c0e399dc3f35.jpg&h=60f9e69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-10-6.08.08_2407683475c0e396fb0fa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-10-6.08.08_2407683475c0e396fb0fa1.jpg&h=790c5551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2012她再次回歸戲劇的舞台，她所演出《惡女羅曼死》讓她惡女的形象更加具體，戲中的澤尻英龍華飾演一個為了人氣、追求完美而不斷整形的巨星，把主角那灰暗思維表現出來。"},{"pid":"a9cc98b9ec6b4936a4ac90b1888676ecb7a91150","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/main201408150758000433232873474_9725387205c0e3d2fe6db0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fmain201408150758000433232873474_9725387205c0e3d2fe6db0.jpg&h=5c0e2c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/-2018-12-10-6.22.50_18370129515c0e3d44c6f1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F-2018-12-10-6.22.50_18370129515c0e3d44c6f1f.jpg&h=3aa84c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澤尻英龍華之後開始演出多部日劇《FIRST CLASS》、《成為母親》等，憑藉自己得演技重新獲得觀眾的喜愛，當然仍有部分人討厭她。對於以前不好的態度，澤尻英龍華唯有頻頻道歉，表示因為當時狀態不好才導致如此失禮。"},{"pid":"188c684bbbbe5e388b9e29752662ee3341ccfe9c","tid":1865828,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢世未見過咁撚柒既戲子<br />\n酒井法子同呢隻臭雞 邊隻臭D?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47762f92c5e8f2a62a4352cb3511d312306ea453","tid":1865828,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:40:31.000Z","msg":"澤尻學生 look <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一去不復返"},{"pid":"4b511b36d0fb3f9b31f32c149582239d227bef4b","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"豬豬同日菁 當年狂搵seed <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f18ccf0f963a00117e70d453ded1b967e3b795af","tid":1865828,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"澤尻早於18歲已沾毒。她透露2004年，當時15歲做模特兒的她，結識18歲的澤尻。當時澤尻已愛留連夜店，又經常與人飲酒，更向她自爆有濫藥惡習。澤尻吸大麻後，會出現怪異行為，更要求她介紹同樣有毒癮的偶像男星。兩人一拍即合，經常一起吸毒後做愛，最多更會一星期見面4日。其後男方更向澤尻表白，但澤尻卻只視對方為炮友而拒絕。"},{"pid":"3fe13f44bcfe42499302f8d54ab4437666f1ef63","tid":1865828,"uid":44951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"一公升同太陽之歌真係最高峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一個衰係自己手上嘅日本藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309bd9749be98b21b999186920094a429f4ec7de","tid":1865828,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb6a108f8ce4e0d9822da5ab156ef407da2f3a2","tid":1865828,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fe13f44bcfe42499302f8d54ab4437666f1ef63","tid":1865828,"uid":44951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"一公升同太陽之歌真係最高峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一個衰係自己手上嘅日本藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"當年紅到聽見有人用ost做鈴聲 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"775ed7ce49c3512faa3f4f59880bc5f8c17c873f","tid":1865828,"uid":345167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18ccf0f963a00117e70d453ded1b967e3b795af","tid":1865828,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"澤尻早於18歲已沾毒。她透露2004年，當時15歲做模特兒的她，結識18歲的澤尻。當時澤尻已愛留連夜店，又經常與人飲酒，更向她自爆有濫藥惡習。澤尻吸大麻後，會出現怪異行為，更要求她介紹同樣有毒癮的偶像男星。兩人一拍即合，經常一起吸毒後做愛，最多更會一星期見面4日。其後男方更向澤尻表白，但澤尻卻只視對方為炮友而拒絕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"想知邊個男星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錦戶亮同赤西仁個堆??"},{"pid":"d3ef